    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h3>New Features</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Watermark overlay — text or image/logo support, three layout styles, adjustable opacity/size/color/position, and live preview</li>
          <li>Preset sequence orchestrator — batch export using multiple presets in sequence</li>
          <li>Per-image results table in export complete dialog</li>
          <li>CSV export of optimization results</li>
          <li>Fixed-size cropping with crop width option</li>
          <li>Live crop dimensions in crop editor</li>
          <li>Update Preset — overwrite existing preset with current settings</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Improvements</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Crop button moved to queue items for easier access</li>
          <li>Sequence and preset management UI refined</li>
          <li>Before/after preview now crops the "before" image to match all crop modes</li>
          <li>Sequence export summary shows per-preset savings</li>
          <li>Quality slider disabled for PNG format (lossless)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed WebP encoding failure on large images at high quality settings</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
